commentary: Starc to Gunathilaka, OUT bowled. There is Starc's customary first-over wicket. What a delivery again. Fuller than a good length - the ideal length. Beaten by the length actually of that

commentary: Zampa to Dilshan, OUT he's gone off a full toss and that's that for Dilshan's ODI career! He came down the track and chipped the low full toss to midwicker where Bailey had to jump a little to catch it over his head. A standing ovation from the spectators, emotional scenes there
